reviews.title: Eggs with a difference. Turkish style.
reviews.text:
Cilbir is eggs with yogurt that is simply unique and delicious. Must have here. 

Shakshuka is not too bad. The right quantity of tomato with eggs. 

Pancakes are super rich. Can barely get past 1 between 2 people. 

Coffees can be served with a shot of caramel that make them super tasty.

The best part, all coffee comes served with Turkish nougat.  

Second best part. There is a kids section at the end that is a life saver if you have a toddler with you.

reviews.title: Best breakfast in Rotterdam
reviews.text: If you are in the market for pancakes these are the best in Rotterdam. They were light yet filling and the yogurt and açai bowls were great too. Wonderful stuff who were friendly and polite.
